fields.description: The High database service provides the highest level of resources to each SQL statement resulting in the highest performance, but supports the fewest number of concurrent SQL statements.
fields.name: High

fields.description: The Low database service provides the least level of resources to each SQL statement, but supports the most number of concurrent SQL statements.
fields.name: Low

fields.description: The Medium database service provides a lower level of resources to each SQL statement potentially resulting a lower level of performance, but supports more concurrent SQL statements.
fields.name: Medium
